title: lolclient.exe is gone and cant open league when i click the ''launch'' button
body:

replies.body: I'd like to help out here but just need a few more little details.  At what percent in the patcher is this happening?  Any additional details, or even screenshot can help a lot.  Let me know!

ehm, i downloaded the whole game 4times, then when i open it now there only is: unspecified error, BUT thats not the main problem, because i added the ''S_OK'' fle and now its working, BUT i can launch the game, everytime i click ''Launch'' nothing happens

I just realized I've already helped you out on another thread.  Unfortunately, there's not much more I can offer here apart from submitting a ticket.  I looked into this for you, and it looks like you're creating quite a bit of tickets.  Doing this can cause a delay in response as well as confusion.  Also, replying to the same ticket constantly can drop you back to the bottom of the queue.  Hang tight and be patient!  We'll respond as soon as possible!
